 [Debug] () Executing DbCommand [Parameters=[""], CommandType='Text', CommandTimeout='30']"
""SELECT [o].[Id], [o].[DateOfOrder], [o].[IsPaid], [o].[Status], [o].[UserId], [a].[Id], [a].[AccessFailedCount], [a].[ConcurrencyStamp], [a].[Email], [a].[EmailConfirmed], [a].[FullName], [a].[LockoutEnabled], [a].[LockoutEnd], [a].[NormalizedEmail], [a].[NormalizedUserName], [a].[PasswordHash], [a].[PhoneNumber], [a].[PhoneNumberConfirmed], [a].[SecurityStamp], [a].[TwoFactorEnabled], [a].[UserName], [t].[ProductId], [t].[OrderId], [t].[Id], [t].[Id0], [t].[Category], [t].[Description], [t].[Name], [t].[Price]
FROM [Orders] AS [o]
LEFT JOIN [AspNetUsers] AS [a] ON [o].[UserId] = [a].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [p].[ProductId], [p].[OrderId], [p].[Id], [p0].[Id] AS [Id0], [p0].[Category], [p0].[Description], [p0].[Name], [p0].[Price]
    FROM [ProductOrders] AS [p]
    INNER JOIN [Products] AS [p0] ON [p].[ProductId] = [p0].[Id]
) AS [t] ON [o].[Id] = [t].[OrderId]
